---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - AI Prompting Playbook">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 min-h-screen relative">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-1/4 w-1/3 h-96 bg-accent-blue/10 rounded-full blur-[150px] -z-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/4 w-1/3 h-96 bg-accent-purple/10 rounded-full blur-[150px] -z-10"></div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        About <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-blue to-accent-purple">AI Prompting Playbook</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Our mission is to democratize expert-level AI interactions by providing a curated library of high-converting, enterprise-grade prompts.
      </p>
      
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 text-left shadow-2xl mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The Problem We're Solving</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none prose-p:text-text-secondary">
          <p>
            As artificial intelligence becomes ubiquitous in the workplace, the primary barrier to entry is no longer access to the technology, but the ability to communicate with it effectively. Most professionals struggle to get consistent, high-quality results from AI models because they lack the time to master prompt engineering.
          </p>
          <p>
            We realized that while there are countless tutorials on "how to prompt," what professionals actually need is a <strong>playbook</strong>—a repository of proven, ready-to-use prompts tailored to their specific roles and tasks.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-bg-secondary/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:border-accent-blue/30 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-blue/20 text-accent-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Tested & Proven</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">Every prompt is rigorously tested against top LLMs for consistency and output quality.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-bg-secondary/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:border-accent-purple/30 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-purple/20 text-accent-purple rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Instant Productivity</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">Copy, paste, and deploy in seconds. Skip the trial-and-error phase entirely.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-bg-secondary/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:border-accent-blue/30 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-blue/20 text-accent-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Enterprise Grade</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">Designed for professionals. Compliance, formatting, and tone are baked right in.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
